== Thingfish::XMLFilter

This is a filter plugin for ThingFish which converts Ruby data structures
into XML strings.

== Dependencies

It requires the CLabs XMLSerial module, available at

 http://clabs.org/clxmlserial.htm

and the ruby Tidy bindings, which can be installed via gem:

 $ sudo gem install tidy

== Configuration

 plugins:
     filters:
         xml:
             tidypath: /path/to/tidy/library.so


=== Config Keys

[tidypath]::
Path to the installed Tidy shared library.  If not specified, uses the OSX default path.



